Package org.zaproxy.zap.session

Class CookieBasedSessionManagementMethodType

java.lang.Object
org.zaproxy.zap.session.SessionManagementMethodType
org.zaproxy.zap.session.CookieBasedSessionManagementMethodType
public class CookieBasedSessionManagementMethodType extends SessionManagementMethodType
The type corresponding to a SessionManagementMethod for web applications that use cookies for session management.
